text: On easthealfe on Cumtunbricgge upon tha lace oth ranwylle, of ranwylle upon thone eastemestan holan weg up to hricgge.
Andlang hrigcges west be ecge on mere, thonon on lyngærstun eastewerdne, thonon on slæw, thone andlang streames on gifle, oth mylenburnna ut scyt up on stream eft to Cumtun bricgge.
